00:01:57.499 --> 00:02:01.710
NASA has been exploring using human hair to
help clean up oil spills.

00:02:01.710 --> 00:02:06.990
In 1989, a hairdresser used clippings from
his salon to create a human hair sponge to

00:02:06.990 --> 00:02:10.580
soak up the Exxon-Valdez spill off the coast
of Alaska.

00:02:10.580 --> 00:02:13.750
The oil clung to the tiny scales in the keratin
and boom!

00:02:13.750 --> 00:02:15.470
An oil sponge was born.

00:02:15.470 --> 00:02:18.200
Hair is also dead useful in fashion and art.

00:02:18.200 --> 00:02:22.840
For example, while doing hair for the movie
Batman Begins, a hairdresser took four-and-a-half

00:02:22.840 --> 00:02:29.319
