this case, the glass was replaced by the perfectly

00:02:39.290 --> 00:02:42.000
renewable resource -- HUMAN HAIRS.

00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:47.189
It has practical purposes for everyday life
too, or... it DID.

00:02:47.189 --> 00:02:51.810
Native Americans created human hair twine
and rope by weaving the strong, straight fibers

00:02:51.810 --> 00:02:53.849
